# 09 — Company

## Company Status

BCSentinel is currently being developed as a founder-led project.

The company is expected to be formally incorporated in **September 2026** under the name **EMERGE**.

EMERGE will serve as the parent company responsible for developing a portfolio of institutional intelligence technologies.

Its first flagship product will be **BCSentinel AI**, an institutional Future Formation Intelligence platform designed to investigate how digital economic systems emerge before their public visibility.

The initial focus of EMERGE will be the successful development, validation and institutional deployment of BCSentinel AI.

Future products may be developed over time as the company's technology platform and institutional intelligence capabilities continue to evolve.

