## Philosophy

The company is built around one fundamental principle:

**Knowledge must be validated before it is accepted.**

Every hypothesis must be investigated.

Every conclusion must be supported by observable evidence.

Every platform capability must be justified through empirical validation.

This philosophy guides both the scientific methodology and the technological architecture of BCSentinel AI.

